file_content.text: Well, yes and no. I found a route into the Deep Prison, but it was a struggle. And unfortunately, the way collapsed behind me.
Bad luck, that. You'll have to find a different route to this level.
What good are you, then?
You are pathetic.
Now now, don't forget, you need me.
I can do it.
Didn't think I needed to hold your hand.
Tell me where to find you.
Where will you be?
Isn't that nice. You want to make sure we can find each other.
Sending the coordinates for our rendezvous. From there, it's quick to Darth Ekkage's cell.
Good luck, Sith. I hope you make it. Can't really do this alone.
Timmns, here.
Darth Ekkage's assassins have been dealt with. Have you managed to accomplish your part?
We better get going. You stop Darth Ekkage's assassins from being released. I'll secure a route deeper into the prison.
That was quite a fight. Thank you.
I don't need your thanks. We have a job to do.
Save the chatter.
Don't mention it. But that's twice I've saved you.
You're welcome. Again.
But who's counting, right?
I need to heal. I'll do a quick patch job. Meet you right there.
You would have been eaten alive if it weren't for me, Jedi.
You'd be dead.
Yeah, I'm a mess. Just let me close some wounds, and I'll be right there.
Get to Darth Ekkage's cell. Stop her from being released, or else everything we've done was a waste.
I'm just catching my breath. Hurry to Darth Ekkage's cell before it's too late.
